    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なぁ、その……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh um, hear me out for a sec...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;の奴に
会ったんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Did you bump into that brat &lt;Arche&gt; by chance?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284464</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;さん？
あ、ええ、会いました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mrs. &lt;Arche&gt;? Yes, we met her.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>元気だったか、あいつ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that annoying brat doing okay?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、元気も元気でさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah! She's livin' and kickin'!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>色々、町の人に
イタズラしてんだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She's been giving some
townsfolk lots of trouble!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イタズラ……？
そうか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She's pranking them? ...Right...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、そのイタズラって
言っても、その、
罪のないことばっかりで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-Well when &lt;Dio&gt; says "trouble",
it really isn't anything ill-intentioned.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかってるって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gotcha.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな悪いこと、
できるような奴じゃないしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's bad for them folks,
but she wouldn't be herself
if she did otherwise.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、あいつが必要以上に
はしゃいでる時ってのは、
寂しい時、なんだよな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, she really had her super fired moments, rightly 
followed by sad moments... What was up with that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>tl check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>２００年後、か……
あのバカ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>200 years later...
That idiot...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……悪ぃ。
&lt;Claus&gt;にも
会ったのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...That's a shame. Anyways,
have you met with &lt;Claus&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285340</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん。
あ、そうだ、
&lt;Rody&gt;にも会ったぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes. Oh, we also met with &lt;Rody&gt; too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285404</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;に？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With &lt;Rody&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん。
ダオスを倒したいって
どこか行っちゃったけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, but she had to leave to
go defeat Dhaos or something.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>過去へ戻ったみたいです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She wanted to return to the
past, by the looks of it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まさか、歴史を
変えるつもりか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Could it be she wants to change history?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>自分が英雄になるため！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maybe she wants to become a hero!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなことして
意味あるのかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wonder, is that really
what she wants to do?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さぁ……あいつ、
ダオス倒すことに
執着してたしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heh...Well that gal always had
an unhealthy obsession with
defeating Dhaos.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そもそも、
何考えてるのか
わからなかったし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Though, I don't have the first idea what
the hell is going through her head...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286268</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしも
よくわかんなかったです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I really don't understand her either...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、面白い姉ちゃんだったぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But hey, she's a funny girl anyways, isn't she?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286424</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ま、それはそうだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, that's that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286488</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルールル！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、うん、行こ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right, let's go!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きゃはぁっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aaaaaah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いてて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ouuuch...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちぇっ……
またやられちったよ、
あいつ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh... Seems I got tricked again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここ……？　どこの洞窟？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wonder... Which cave is this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuuru?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_120_020_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ううん……
何か聞こえた気がして……
気のせいかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh...I was sure I heard
something just now...
Am I imagining things?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
